test_all_one_range:
assert [1, 1, 1] == [1, 1]
  
  Left contains one more item: 1
  
  Full diff:
    [
        1,
        1,
  +     1,
    ]
test_odd_same_number:
assert [-11, -11, -11] == [-11, -11]
  
  Left contains one more item: -11
  
  Full diff:
    [
        -11,
        -11,
  +     -11,
    ]
